public class PositionAndGMSReferencing
extends com.kuka.roboticsAPI.applicationModel.RoboticsAPIApplication

This application can be used as template for Lbr iiwa Position and GMS Referencing. The safety needs exactly 10 measurements to perform a successful GMS Referencing. The time between two measurements must be less than 15 seconds.
